title: Haris Laitinen
text:
Haris Laitinen (born 5 December 1984) is a <a href="Sweden">Swedish</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who played for <a href="Enskede%20IK">Enskede IK</a>.
Career.
He signed for <a href="Assyriska%20F%C3%B6reningen">Assyriska Föreningen</a> after leaving <a href="Hammarby%20IF">Hammarby IF</a> in December 2009.
He went to Hammarby from <a href="Hammarby%20Talang%20FF">Hammarby Talang FF</a> for the 2004 season.
After the 2006 season with <a href="IFK%20Norrk%C3%B6ping">IFK Norrköping</a> on loan, he returned to Hammarby.
